To delete a todo, click on the todo you want to delete from the list. Then click on DELETE SELECTED TODO. Confirm the deletion by clicking on OK.

To access the CRUD functions through the REST API, open a new tab in your Ib browser and navigate to http://localhost:8000/api/todos/. This will display a list of todos for the current user.
To create a new todo, click on the CREATE button at the top of the page. Enter the task details and click on SAVE.
